      "right_now_cig_smoke_50cents": "How many cigarettes would you smoke RIGHT NOW if they were 50� each? [$10/pack]",
      "right_now_cig_smoke_1dollar": "How many cigarettes would you smoke RIGHT NOW if they were $1 each? [$20/pack]",
